00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:53,080
 So that's what we do.

41
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:55,120
 So when this Python program starts,

42
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:58,800
 it's going to sit there and wait in an infinite loop

