00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:01,280
 for incoming requests.

44
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:03,920
 So the first thing we do is we're going to make a socket.

45
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:05,880
 This looks very much like the time we made.

